defaultRentals.title: Highly desirable 2 bdr/2 bth luxurious condo in Nuuanu
defaultRentals.description:
Highly desirable 2 bdr/2 bth luxurious condo in Nuuanu. Only 4 units per floor. Spacious layout with large lanais overlooking the gorgeous views of the city, ocean, and mountains. Central AC and washer/dryer inside unit. Includes 2 pkg(tandem). Secured bldg. with nice amenities featuring a BBQ area, gym, and pool. Prime location close to downtown, Ala Moana, Kakaako, shopping centers, and freeway access. No pets.

1 year lease. Water, sewer, basic cable and internet included. No pets.
